 https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AltJ_MadCool2022_AFord-63506-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AltJ_MadCool2022_AFord-63506-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AltJ_MadCool2022_AFord-63506-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AltJ_MadCool2022_AFord-63506-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alt-j">Alt-J</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/JOE-NEWMAN">乔·纽曼 (Joe Newman)</a>向<em>NME</em>透露了他的首张个人专辑的计划，该专辑受到“Americana、Motown、soul”的影响。</p><p>纽曼昨天（5 月 23 日星期四）在 Ivor Novellos 的红地毯上接受<em>NME</em>采访时，他告诉我们，在他们广受好评的第四张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/alt-j-the-dream-album-four-review-3154349">The梦</a>&#39;。</p><p> “我现在正在做一些个人工作，”他说。 “我去了洛杉矶，一直与制片人卡洛斯·德拉·加尔萨（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/PARAMORE">《帕拉莫尔》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-linda-lindas">《琳达琳达》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/m83">《M83》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cold-war-kids">《冷战孩子</a>》）合作。过去几个月我们在一起度过了一些时间，我们正在讨论各种想法。这确实是一次令人振奋的全新体验。我绝对喜欢它。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C7WpWiUpWX-/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" backgro